  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.9.9">
<l>maṟaiyārum peruvēḷvik koḻumpukaipōy vaḷarnteṅkum</l>
<l>niṟaiyāra vāṉmūṭum nīṭcelvat tirunaṟaiyūr</l>
<l>piṟaiyāruñ caṭaiyāṉum piramaṉumuṉ toḻutētta</l>
<l>iṟaiyāki niṉṟāṉṟa ṉiṇaiyaṭiyē yaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirunaṟaiyūr of vast wealth where thick smoke</l>
<l rend="indent">from great Vedic sacrifices</l>
<l>Obscures the sky, expanding, going everywhere as it spreads in profusion,</l>
<l>O heart, take refuge at both feet of the one who endures as god,</l>
<l>So that the one in whose matted locks the crescent abides and Brahmā,</l>
<l rend="indent">bowing before [him], praise [him].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
